Well Report Tracking Number: 136815. USGS Site Number: 293456098304901. During a dye tracing test in 2006, this well was found to be co-mingling between the Glen Rose (Trinity) and the Edwards BFZ. In November 2014 a packer was installed at 420 ft to isolate the Glen Rose (below 420 ft) and the Edwards BFZ (above 420 ft); making this a dual completion well. All data prior to November 2014 is a mixture of Glen Rose (Trinity) and Edwards BFZ. All data assigned to SWN 6828608 after Nov 2014 is exclusively Edwards BFZ. State Well Number 6828614 was assigned to the Glen Rose Trinity portion
